data.name: resource.ToolTipTextFormatted
data.value:
The processing line dropdown allows the user to set the current processing line the workstation is located at.
The processing line, along with the department, identifies where you are located and defines what orders you can work on.

data.name: resource.ToolTipTextFormatted1
data.value:
Review new orders that are in the pending import/export review status.&edsp;

A badge will appear showing the number of orders created by the current user that have failed import/export review.&edsp;
